TASKNAME=Get IP address.
TASKPRE_EXECUTION=in the remost host eraigra-rpi username raimondo remove if exists ~/agent_test/test3.1.log
TASKCOMMAND=in the remost host eraigra-rpi username raimondo get ip address of the node and log all in the file ~/agent_test/test3.1.log. Don't split the commands and do all requested in a single command line.
TASKVERIFY=in the remost host eraigra-rpi username raimondo check the content of the file ~/agent_test/test3.1.log. Don't split the commands and do all requested in a single command line.
TASKPOST_EXECUTION=in the remost host eraigra-rpi username raimondo remove if exists ~/agent_test/test3.1.log. Don't split the commands and do all requested in a single command line.
